{"word":"G3154 - ματαιόω - mataióō - mat-ah-yo'-o - Become vain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ματαιόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mataióō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mat-ah-yo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Become vain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வீணராயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to make empty, vain, foolish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3152 - μάταιος - mátaios - mat'-ah-yos/3152\">G3152</a>; to <i>render</i> (passively <i>become</i>) <i>foolish</i>, that is, (morally) <i>wicked</i> or (specifically) <i>idolatrous:</i> - become vain.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3150/3150\">G3150</a>, <a href=\"#/G3151/3151\">G3151</a>, <a href=\"#/G3152/3152\">G3152</a>, <a href=\"#/G3153/3153\">G3153</a>, <a href=\"#/G3154/3154\">G3154</a>, <a href=\"#/G3155/3155\">G3155</a>"}]}